data.description: This three bedroom one and half bath home features an open concept, large backyard and an amazing centralized location. A well maintained property filled with updates galore. Feel comfortable with the new stove, newer furnace, all new lightning, updated home insulation, as well as new bathroom and kitchen fixtures. Enjoy this light and bright space with fresh paint throughout, new flooring, new kitchen countertop and updated cabinets. Easy access to highways, downtown, shopping, and room for your furry friends makes this home a great option and a must see.
